<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Telecom Churn Analysis Dashboard</title>
<style>
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: #f8f7f4; color: #1a1a18; padding: 24px; }
  h1 { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4px; color: #1a1a18; }
  .subtitle { font-size: 13px; color: #6b6b66; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .section-title { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; color: #888780; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; margin: 0 0 10px; }
  .cards { display: flex; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 20px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .card { flex: 1; min-width: 120px; background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e0ded8; border-radius: 12px; padding: 14px 16px; }
  .card .val { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; color: #1a1a18; }
  .card .lbl { font-size: 12px; color: #888780; margin-top: 2px; }
  .chart-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  @media (max-width: 600px) { .chart-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .chart-box.wide { grid-column: span 1; } }
  .chart-box { background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e0ded8; border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px; }
  .chart-box.wide { grid-column: span 2; }
  .chart-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #1a1a18; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .bar-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .bar-label { font-size: 12px; color: #6b6b66; width: 70px; flex-shrink: 0; text-align: right; }
  .bar-track { flex: 1; height: 18px; background: #f1efe8; border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; }
  .bar-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 4px; transition: width 1s ease; }
  .bar-pct { font-size: 11px; width: 36px; flex-shrink: 0; font-weight: 600; }
  .legend { display: flex; gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .legend-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px; font-size: 12px; color: #6b6b66; }
  .dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .insight-box { background: #faeeda; border: 1px solid #fac775; border-radius: 12px; padding: 14px 16px; display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: flex-start; }
  .insight-box .icon { font-size: 16px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
  .insight-box .text { font-size: 13px; color: #412402; line-height: 1.6; }
  .insight-box .text strong { font-weight: 600; }
  .hist-wrap { display: flex; align-items: flex-end; gap: 4px; height: 90px; padding: 0 4px; }
  .hist-col { flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 2px; }
  .hist-bar { width: 100%; border-radius: 3px 3px 0 0; transition: height 1s ease; }
  .hist-lbl { font-size: 10px; color: #aaa; margin-top: 2px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<h1>📊 Telecom Customer Churn Analysis</h1>
<p class="subtitle">Exploratory data analysis — key churn drivers and risk segments</p>

<p class="section-title">Overview</p>
<div class="cards">
  <div class="card"><div class="val" style="color:#D85A30">26.5%</div><div class="lbl">Overall churn rate</div></div>
  <div class="card"><div class="val">7,043</div><div class="lbl">Total customers</div></div>
  <div class="card"><div class="val" style="color:#1D9E75">73.5%</div><div class="lbl">Retention rate</div></div>
  <div class="card"><div class="val">$64.8</div><div class="lbl">Avg monthly charge</div></div>
</div>

<div class="chart-grid">

  <div class="chart-box">
    <div class="chart-title">Churn by contract type</div>
    <div class="legend">
      <div class="legend-item"><div class="dot" style="background:#D85A30"></div> Churned</div>
      <div class="legend-item"><div class="dot" style="background:#1D9E75"></div> Retained</div>
    </div>
    <div class="bar-row">
      <div class="bar-label">Monthly</div>
      <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill" style="width:42%;background:#D85A30"></div></div>
      <div class="bar-pct" style="color:#D85A30">42%</div>
    </div>
    <div class="bar-row">
      <div class="bar-label">Annual</div>
      <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill" style="width:11%;background:#EF9F27"></div></div>
      <div class="bar-pct" style="color:#EF9F27">11%</div>
    </div>
    <div class="bar-row">
      <div class="bar-label">Biennial</div>
      <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill" style="width:3%;background:#1D9E75"></div></div>
      <div class="bar-pct" style="color:#1D9E75">3%</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="chart-box">
    <div class="chart-title">Churn by tenure group</div>
    <div class="bar-row">
      <div class="bar-label">0–3 mo</div>
      <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill" style="width:55%;background:#D85A30"></div></div>
      <div class="bar-pct" style="color:#D85A30">55%</div>
    </div>
    <div class="bar-row">
      <div class="bar-label">4–12 mo</div>
      <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill" style="width:35%;background:#EF9F27"></div></div>
      <div class="bar-pct" style="color:#EF9F27">35%</div>
    </div>
    <div class="bar-row">
      <div class="bar-label">13–24 mo</div>
      <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill" style="width:24%;background:#BA7517"></div></div>
      <div class="bar-pct" style="color:#BA7517">24%</div>
    </div>
    <div class="bar-row">
      <div class="bar-label">25–48 mo</div>
      <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill" style="width:14%;background:#639922"></div></div>
      <div class="bar-pct" style="color:#639922">14%</div>
    </div>
    <div class="bar-row">
      <div class="bar-label">49+ mo</div>
      <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill" style="width:6%;background:#1D9E75"></div></div>
      <div class="bar-pct" style="color:#1D9E75">6%</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="chart-box wide">
    <div class="chart-title">Monthly charges distribution — churned vs retained</div>
    <div class="hist-wrap">
      <div class="hist-col"><div class="hist-bar" style="height:48px;background:#1D9E75;opacity:0.7"></div><div class="hist-bar" style="height:8px;background:#D85A30;opacity:0.85"></div><div class="hist-lbl">≤20</div></div>
      <div class="hist-col"><div class="hist-bar" style="height:62px;background:#1D9E75;opacity:0.7"></div><div class="hist-bar" style="height:14px;background:#D85A30;opacity:0.85"></div><div class="hist-lbl">20–35</div></div>
      <div class="hist-col"><div class="hist-bar" style="height:50px;background:#1D9E75;opacity:0.7"></div><div class="hist-bar" style="height:12px;background:#D85A30;opacity:0.85"></div><div class="hist-lbl">35–50</div></div>
      <div class="hist-col"><div class="hist-bar" style="height:44px;background:#1D9E75;opacity:0.7"></div><div class="hist-bar" style="height:20px;background:#D85A30;opacity:0.85"></div><div class="hist-lbl">50–65</div></div>
      <div class="hist-col"><div class="hist-bar" style="height:30px;background:#1D9E75;opacity:0.7"></div><div class="hist-bar" style="height:36px;background:#D85A30;opacity:0.85"></div><div class="hist-lbl">65–80</div></div>
      <div class="hist-col"><div class="hist-bar" style="height:22px;background:#1D9E75;opacity:0.7"></div><div class="hist-bar" style="height:58px;background:#D85A30;opacity:0.85"></div><div class="hist-lbl">80–95</div></div>
      <div class="hist-col"><div class="hist-bar" style="height:16px;background:#1D9E75;opacity:0.7"></div><div class="hist-bar" style="height:68px;background:#D85A30;opacity:0.85"></div><div class="hist-lbl">95–110</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="legend" style="margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:0">
      <div class="legend-item"><div class="dot" style="background:#1D9E75;opacity:0.7"></div> Retained</div>
      <div class="legend-item"><div class="dot" style="background:#D85A30;opacity:0.85"></div> Churned — higher charges = more churn</div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<div class="insight-box">
  <div class="icon">⚠️</div>
  <div class="text">
    <strong>Key finding:</strong> Customers on <strong>Monthly contracts with 0–3 months tenure</strong> have the highest churn risk — over half churn before month 4. Churned customers also tend to pay <strong>higher monthly charges</strong> ($80–$110 range). Improving early engagement and offering incentives to switch to annual contracts could significantly reduce churn.
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
